text.tspan: Israel: Share of adults that have received one or two doses of the
Share of adults in each age group that received at least one, or both doses of the COVID-19 vaccine. Numbers that have
previously recovered from COVID-19 are also included in this share.
Data source: Rossman, Shilo, Meir, Gorfine, Shalit & Segal (2021). Patterns of COVID-19 pandemic dynamics following
deployment of a broad national immunization program.
